longBusinessSummary: hmvod Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the provision of professional services and over-the-top (OTT) services in the People's Republic of China. The Professional Services segment offers information technology engineering and technical support services, including financial valuation and IT services. The OTT Services segment produces and distributes films, television programs, and music production on OTT platforms. It also provides services and solutions on cyber security; and multi-media related and content services. hmvod Limited is based in Chai Wan, Hong Kong.
